  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>From its prime position on the Corso dell’Imperatrice, Lolli Palace is at the heart of Sanremo’s luxurious history. Surrounded by luscious palms and overlooking the emerald bay, all of the resorts restaurants, bars, museums, galleries and even casino reminiscent of its neighbouring Montecarlo are all within walking distance.</p>]]></listingDescription>
